text: Ousmane Diakité (born 25 July 2000) is a Malian footballer currently playing for Rheindorf Altach on loan from Red Bull Salzburg. ==Club career== Diakité started his career with the Malian side Yeelen Olympique. In July 2018 he signed a contract with FC Red Bull Salzburg in Austria till May 2023. He also plays for the feeder team FC Liefering. His played his first match for FC Liefering on July 27, 2018 against SV Horn. In this match he was excluded after two yellow cards in minute 39 and 92. ==National team== With the Malian U17 he became runner-up in the world championships 2015.
